{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d135050b3c","title":"接见谢富治同志时的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6e0b69e537","index":0,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":19,"articleId":"d135050b3c","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"谢富治","id":"93cca4665d","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961-1968卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"99cc826773","type":"paragraph","text":"与X同志的一段对斋","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d135050b3c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a28280a1a7","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年四月）主席问：你们说是北京的大学大联合了，成立了红代会，很好呀！那三个司合部呢？","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d135050b3c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5e39268260","type":"paragraph","text":"答：没有了，都取消了。主席：啊，为什么要取消呀？我才不相信呢！已经取滑了","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d135050b3c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9d42b3623f","type":"paragraph","text":"（摘自周恩来同志1967年4月18日在广州群众组织座谈会的讲话）关于重管间题","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d135050b3c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"220c06c25c","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年四月）军管太少了。刘邓派工作组是压迫革命、反对群众，我们军管是支持革命的。","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d135050b3c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c188f14032","type":"paragraph","text":"（摘自谢富治副总理四月十八日讲话）关于革命派的大联合","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d135050b3c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"43413bbdea","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年四月）","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d135050b3c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fcbe456824","type":"paragraph","text":"目前全国斗争形势很好，成绩很大，经验很多，全国都在前进中。革命派在优势情况下，可按系统、按部门、按单位实行大联合。但要注意保守派把造反派吃掉，不要用解散革命造反派的办法实行大联合。","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d135050b3c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4128ba8b7c","type":"paragraph","text":"接见富治同志时的款柔","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d135050b3c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"907b9eb443","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年四月十九日下午）我配贺你，祝贺这次大会的成功。请代向全北京市革命造反派祝贺。致敬电是全世界无产者联合超来的大宣言，就不要再搞宜言了。","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d135050b3c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"848ab33ca5","type":"paragraph","text":"青年人要参加你们的工作，使前辈人不脱离群众，使青年人得到。青年人不能脱产，这样会造成脱离群众的，要牛官牛民。","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d135050b3c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"36874e9c27","type":"paragraph","text":"北京的形势还有反复，无政府主义就是机会主义的惩。要不怕犯错误，各种反动的观点和反动的群众组织是极少数的。就是反动组织也要做工作，但是还得斗争。","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d135050b3c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e0b34f1c91","type":"paragraph","text":"无政府主义是对机会主义的惩","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d135050b3c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"786b391767","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年四月）","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d135050b3c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ccfd39b95a","type":"paragraph","text":"过去的八条，现在的十条结合超来是对的。左派超来了，对立面也超来了，这也不要紧，有点反复有好处。无政府主义是对机会主义的惩留，要走向反面。","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d135050b3c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bc993135f5","type":"paragraph","text":"要把所有的联动放出来。·302。","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d135050b3c","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":315,"end":315}},"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5d4e752684","type":"paragraph","text":"青年人要参加你们的工作，使前辈人不脱离群众，使青年人得到锻炼。青年人不能脱产，这样会造成脱离群众的，要半官半民。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"d135050b3c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9cc7c0932c","type":"title","text":"接见谢富治同志时的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"d135050b3c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aac6b4dcd2","type":"paragraph","text":"北京的形势还有反复，无政府主义就是机会主义的惩罚。要不怕犯错误，各种反动的观点和反动的群众组织是极少数的。就是反动组织也要做工作，但是还得斗争。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"d135050b3c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b07d6a6e32","type":"paragraph","text":"我祝贺你，祝贺这次大会的成功。请代向全北京市革命造反派祝贺。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"d135050b3c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c4f9afafe5","type":"paragraph","text":"致敬电是全世界无产者联合起来的大宣言，就不要再搞宣言了。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"d135050b3c","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":581,"end":581}}}},"__N_SSG":true}